Text.SourceString: Good day. How may I help you?
Text.LocalizedString: Good day. How may I help you?

Text.SourceString: Please don’t hesitate to ask for my assistance whenever you’re in Pufferfish Corporation’s Coral Island office.
Text.LocalizedString: Please don’t hesitate to ask for my assistance whenever you’re in Pufferfish Corporation’s Coral Island office.

Text.SourceString: I’ve seen all the wonderful things Pufferfish has done for communities.//<portrait=normal>I believe you can see the results of those projects in the meeting room behind me.
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve seen all the wonderful things Pufferfish has done for communities.//<portrait=normal>I believe you can see the results of those projects in the meeting room behind me.

Text.SourceString: Are you looking for something in particular?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you looking for something in particular?

Text.SourceString: Over to my right is our employee working area. Behind me is the manager’s office, currently occupied by our branch manager, <NPCName>Karen</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Over to my right is our employee working area. Behind me is the manager’s office, currently occupied by our branch manager, <NPCName>Karen</>.

Text.SourceString: The results of some of our past projects are on display in the meeting area. Feel free to look around!
Text.LocalizedString: The results of some of our past projects are on display in the meeting area. Feel free to look around!

Text.SourceString: Our posters aren’t for sale.//<portrait=surprised>If you wish to purchase one, I can pass on your interest. We’ll get back to you if anything changes.
Text.LocalizedString: Our posters aren’t for sale.//<portrait=surprised>If you wish to purchase one, I can pass on your interest. We’ll get back to you if anything changes.

Text.SourceString: I love working at Pufferfish.//We’re all family here.
Text.LocalizedString: I love working at Pufferfish.//We’re all family here.

Text.SourceString: I can’t remember the last time I used my paid time off.//<portrait=happy>I don’t need it. I just need to work and work and work.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t remember the last time I used my paid time off.//<portrait=happy>I don’t need it. I just need to work and work and work.

Text.SourceString: The temperature here is the same all year long.//It’s perfect.
Text.LocalizedString: The temperature here is the same all year long.//It’s perfect.

Text.SourceString: We have big windows in our break room.//So it feels like you’re outside, but you’re not.
Text.LocalizedString: We have big windows in our break room.//So it feels like you’re outside, but you’re not.

Text.SourceString: Pufferfish is the perfect place to kickstart your career in the oil industry.
Text.LocalizedString: Pufferfish is the perfect place to kickstart your career in the oil industry.

Text.SourceString: Every Friday, we’re allowed to wear casual clothing, like jeans.//Nobody does, but it shows how casual the work environment is here.
Text.LocalizedString: Every Friday, we’re allowed to wear casual clothing, like jeans.//Nobody does, but it shows how casual the work environment is here.

Text.SourceString: If I dedicate all my time to work, Pufferfish will reward me for it.//The company cares so much about our well-being.
Text.LocalizedString: If I dedicate all my time to work, Pufferfish will reward me for it.//The company cares so much about our well-being.

Text.SourceString: The area downstairs is for employees only.//You can’t go there. I’m sorry.
Text.LocalizedString: The area downstairs is for employees only.//You can’t go there. I’m sorry.

Text.SourceString: We’re not allowed to receive any gifts here.//<portrait=happy>If you want to show your appreciation to Pufferfish Corp, I suggest sending it directly to our main office.
Text.LocalizedString: We’re not allowed to receive any gifts here.//<portrait=happy>If you want to show your appreciation to Pufferfish Corp, I suggest sending it directly to our main office.

Text.SourceString: We don’t encourage music here.//<portrait=normal>Distractions of any kind are prohibited.
Text.LocalizedString: We don’t encourage music here.//<portrait=normal>Distractions of any kind are prohibited.

Text.SourceString: I’m looking forward to your joining our corporation one day.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m looking forward to your joining our corporation one day.

Text.SourceString: Welcome to Pufferfish Corp. How may I assist you today?
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome to Pufferfish Corp. How may I assist you today?

Text.SourceString: Welcome to the recreation center! If you need any assistance, I'm here to help.
Text.LocalizedString: Welcome to the recreation center! If you need any assistance, I'm here to help.

Text.SourceString: Greetings! It's great to see you today, <PlayerName>$player</>.//How are things going at the farm?
Text.LocalizedString: Greetings! It's great to see you today, <PlayerName>$player</>.//How are things going at the farm?

Text.SourceString: Good day, <PlayerName>$player</>. If you require any help or information, please feel free to ask me.
Text.LocalizedString: Good day, <PlayerName>$player</>. If you require any help or information, please feel free to ask me.

Text.SourceString: Oh! Welcome to the recreation center. How can I assist you today, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh! Welcome to the recreation center. How can I assist you today, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: Feel free to explore our facilities. We have a bakery shop, a gym, mini golf, and a theater for your enjoyment.
Text.LocalizedString: Feel free to explore our facilities. We have a bakery shop, a gym, mini golf, and a theater for your enjoyment.

Text.SourceString: Looking for a place to relax? Our theater offers a variety of shows, perfect for unwinding after a busy day.
Text.LocalizedString: Looking for a place to relax? Our theater offers a variety of shows, perfect for unwinding after a busy day.

Text.SourceString: If you're looking for fresh pastries, our bakery shop, managed by Eva, is just around the corner. She makes each item with great care.
Text.LocalizedString: If you're looking for fresh pastries, our bakery shop, managed by Eva, is just around the corner. She makes each item with great care.

Text.SourceString: Maybe you and I could challenge each other at minigolf sometime?
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe you and I could challenge each other at minigolf sometime?

Text.SourceString: I'm here to make sure that your experience here is nothing short of excellent.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm here to make sure that your experience here is nothing short of excellent.

Text.SourceString: Each section of the garden is lovingly cared for by members of our community.//<portrait=happy>It's a showcase of local green thumbs at work.
Text.LocalizedString: Each section of the garden is lovingly cared for by members of our community.//<portrait=happy>It's a showcase of local green thumbs at work.

Text.SourceString: I always recommend a visit to the garden. Whether you're a gardener or not, it's a beautiful and calming place.
Text.LocalizedString: I always recommend a visit to the garden. Whether you're a gardener or not, it's a beautiful and calming place.

Text.SourceString: Oh, I'm sorry, but I can't accept any gifts. It's against the rules.//<portrait=happy>But thank you for thinking of me!
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, I'm sorry, but I can't accept any gifts. It's against the rules.//<portrait=happy>But thank you for thinking of me!

Text.SourceString: As a farmer, you might find our community garden particularly interesting. We'd love to hear any tips you have for us.
Text.LocalizedString: As a farmer, you might find our community garden particularly interesting. We'd love to hear any tips you have for us.

Text.SourceString: Rainy days can be a bit gloomy, don't you think? I prefer when the sun is shining.
Text.LocalizedString: Rainy days can be a bit gloomy, don't you think? I prefer when the sun is shining.

Text.SourceString: Rainy days can be a bit gloomy, don't you think? I prefer when the sun is shining.
Text.LocalizedString: Rainy days can be a bit gloomy, don't you think? I prefer when the sun is shining.

Text.SourceString: I know rain is important for the garden, but I just can't seem to enjoy these wet days.
Text.LocalizedString: I know rain is important for the garden, but I just can't seem to enjoy these wet days.

Text.SourceString: Rain again? It makes everything so damp and muddy.
Text.LocalizedString: Rain again? It makes everything so damp and muddy.

Text.SourceString: Rain again? It makes everything so damp and muddy.
Text.LocalizedString: Rain again? It makes everything so damp and muddy.

Text.SourceString: Snow has its charm, but it sure does make getting around a bit challenging.
Text.LocalizedString: Snow has its charm, but it sure does make getting around a bit challenging.

Text.SourceString: Snow days can be fun, but they also mean a lot of shoveling and slippery paths.
Text.LocalizedString: Snow days can be fun, but they also mean a lot of shoveling and slippery paths.

Text.SourceString: The children here seem to love the snow. I saw them playing near the community center.
Text.LocalizedString: The children here seem to love the snow. I saw them playing near the community center.

Text.SourceString: During the Winter, the sea takes on a whole new character. It's more serene and peaceful.//The view from my room at the inn is stunning!
Text.LocalizedString: During the Winter, the sea takes on a whole new character. It's more serene and peaceful.//The view from my room at the inn is stunning!

Text.SourceString: I've made some friends here, like Eva. She's really kind and even showed me how to bake bread.//<portrait=happy>It's a simple process, but so fulfilling.
Text.LocalizedString: I've made some friends here, like Eva. She's really kind and even showed me how to bake bread.//<portrait=happy>It's a simple process, but so fulfilling.

Text.SourceString: Working here has been more enjoyable for me than at Pufferfish. People here are just friendlier.
Text.LocalizedString: Working here has been more enjoyable for me than at Pufferfish. People here are just friendlier.

Text.SourceString: I've worn the Pufferfish uniform for most of my adult life.//It feels good to finally wear different clothes.
Text.LocalizedString: I've worn the Pufferfish uniform for most of my adult life.//It feels good to finally wear different clothes.

Text.SourceString: When Pufferfish decided to leave the island, I realized I had fallen in love with this place.//<portrait=normal>So, I decided to stay.
Text.LocalizedString: When Pufferfish decided to leave the island, I realized I had fallen in love with this place.//<portrait=normal>So, I decided to stay.

Text.SourceString: Everyone at the inn has been incredibly kind. It's been a wonderful experience living there.
Text.LocalizedString: Everyone at the inn has been incredibly kind. It's been a wonderful experience living there.

Text.SourceString: I'm not much of a gardener, to be honest.//<portrait=happy>I admire those who have the knack for it though...like you!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not much of a gardener, to be honest.//<portrait=happy>I admire those who have the knack for it though...like you!

Text.SourceString: The inn does get quite cold during the Winter, but oh well, it's affordable to stay there.
Text.LocalizedString: The inn does get quite cold during the Winter, but oh well, it's affordable to stay there.

Text.SourceString: Gardening has never been my strong suit. I'm better at appreciating plants than growing them.
Text.LocalizedString: Gardening has never been my strong suit. I'm better at appreciating plants than growing them.

Text.SourceString: I tried making a pizza for myself yesterday. I forgot it was in the oven and ended up burning it.
Text.LocalizedString: I tried making a pizza for myself yesterday. I forgot it was in the oven and ended up burning it.

Text.SourceString: The Spring here is my favorite season. It's the perfect balance, not too cold and not too hot.
Text.LocalizedString: The Spring here is my favorite season. It's the perfect balance, not too cold and not too hot.

Text.SourceString: I heard you helped build this place. Is that true?//<portrait=normal>That's amazing. You've achieved so much.
Text.LocalizedString: I heard you helped build this place. Is that true?//<portrait=normal>That's amazing. You've achieved so much.

Text.SourceString: I think I'll stop by the coffee shop tomorrow before work. A cup of coffee would be a great start to the day.
Text.LocalizedString: I think I'll stop by the coffee shop tomorrow before work. A cup of coffee would be a great start to the day.

Text.SourceString: Let me know if there's anything I can do to make your visit more enjoyable.
Text.LocalizedString: Let me know if there's anything I can do to make your visit more enjoyable.

Text.SourceString: If you're looking for specific facilities, like the gym or mini-golf, I'd be happy to direct you.
Text.LocalizedString: If you're looking for specific facilities, like the gym or mini-golf, I'd be happy to direct you.

Text.SourceString: Our bakery has some new treats on offer. They're a must-try if you have a sweet tooth.
Text.LocalizedString: Our bakery has some new treats on offer. They're a must-try if you have a sweet tooth.

Text.SourceString: Feel free to relax in our lounge area.
Text.LocalizedString: Feel free to relax in our lounge area.

Text.SourceString: The day's perfect for a round of mini-golf. Would you like to book a tee time?
Text.LocalizedString: The day's perfect for a round of mini-golf. Would you like to book a tee time?

Text.SourceString: Just a reminder, we have a gym right over there if you're looking to get in a workout.
Text.LocalizedString: Just a reminder, we have a gym right over there if you're looking to get in a workout.

Text.SourceString: I spoke to Rafael the other day at the inn. He's adorable and really kind.//Do you know if he's...single?
Text.LocalizedString: I spoke to Rafael the other day at the inn. He's adorable and really kind.//Do you know if he's...single?

Text.SourceString: I often see Rafael hanging out with Valentina at the inn.//<portrait=normal>They play together and seem to enjoy each other's company. He seems like a sweet guy.
Text.LocalizedString: I often see Rafael hanging out with Valentina at the inn.//<portrait=normal>They play together and seem to enjoy each other's company. He seems like a sweet guy.

Text.SourceString: Rafael fixed the light in my room the other day.//<portrait=concerned>I tried to give him some money for it, but he refused. I hope I didn't offend him.
Text.LocalizedString: Rafael fixed the light in my room the other day.//<portrait=concerned>I tried to give him some money for it, but he refused. I hope I didn't offend him.

Text.SourceString: Oh hey, it's you! Remember me? I used to work at Pufferfish Corp, but not anymore.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh hey, it's you! Remember me? I used to work at Pufferfish Corp, but not anymore.

Text.SourceString: I decided to quit when they moved off the island. Great to run into you again!
Text.LocalizedString: I decided to quit when they moved off the island. Great to run into you again!

Text.SourceString: I don't like talking about my time at Pufferfish.//I feel like it's part of my past, and it should stay there.
Text.LocalizedString: I don't like talking about my time at Pufferfish.//I feel like it's part of my past, and it should stay there.

Text.SourceString: I've been thinking about getting a haircut. I've heard Erika does wonders with long hair.//<portrait=happy>Maybe I should pay her a visit.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been thinking about getting a haircut. I've heard Erika does wonders with long hair.//<portrait=happy>Maybe I should pay her a visit.

Text.SourceString: Emily recently did a touch-up on my hair tips. It took a couple of hours, but I absolutely love the results.//<portrait=happy>What do you think?
Text.LocalizedString: Emily recently did a touch-up on my hair tips. It took a couple of hours, but I absolutely love the results.//<portrait=happy>What do you think?

Text.SourceString: My stomach has been feeling a bit off. I'm worried it might be from the sushi I ate yesterday.//I wasn't sure how fresh it was.
Text.LocalizedString: My stomach has been feeling a bit off. I'm worried it might be from the sushi I ate yesterday.//I wasn't sure how fresh it was.

Text.SourceString: I think I should head to the clinic after this.
Text.LocalizedString: I think I should head to the clinic after this.

Text.SourceString: I considered renting a room at the ranch near the forest, but being that close to the forest kind of scares me.
Text.LocalizedString: I considered renting a room at the ranch near the forest, but being that close to the forest kind of scares me.

Text.SourceString: Though, now that I think about it, the price was half of what I pay at the inn. It was actually a steal.
Text.LocalizedString: Though, now that I think about it, the price was half of what I pay at the inn. It was actually a steal.

Text.SourceString: The tavern gets pretty lively at night. It's quite the spot for evening entertainment.
Text.LocalizedString: The tavern gets pretty lively at night. It's quite the spot for evening entertainment.

Text.SourceString: I went to a live performance at the tavern last weekend. Theo was on stage, and he was fantastic!
Text.LocalizedString: I went to a live performance at the tavern last weekend. Theo was on stage, and he was fantastic!

Text.SourceString: My favorite part about living here is probably my beachfront room.//I couldn’t have afforded a place right on the water back in the city.
Text.LocalizedString: My favorite part about living here is probably my beachfront room.//I couldn’t have afforded a place right on the water back in the city.

Text.SourceString: I'm thinking of baking a cake for Alice and Suki at the inn. Their birthday is coming up soon, and I think it'd be a nice gesture.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm thinking of baking a cake for Alice and Suki at the inn. Their birthday is coming up soon, and I think it'd be a nice gesture.

Text.SourceString: Maybe I should just buy it instead. I'm a bit worried that if I make it, it might not turn out well.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe I should just buy it instead. I'm a bit worried that if I make it, it might not turn out well.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, I see Rafael at the cemetery alone. I'm not sure if I should approach him or just let him be.//I've thought maybe he needs a friend.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, I see Rafael at the cemetery alone. I'm not sure if I should approach him or just let him be.//I've thought maybe he needs a friend.

Text.SourceString: It's hard to find red eyeshadow around here.
Text.LocalizedString: It's hard to find red eyeshadow around here.

Text.SourceString: I got my suit set from the White Flamingo. They have an amazing selection there!
Text.LocalizedString: I got my suit set from the White Flamingo. They have an amazing selection there!
